data.description: Introducing your ideal residence at 130 E Lake Deer Dr., situated in the tranquil Winter Haven, FL neighborhood. This exquisite home offers not just a place to live but a haven of comfort and serenity. Upon entering, you'll find a brand new roof, included in the listing price, ready to protect your new beginnings, providing peace of mind as you approach the closing date. This remarkable home is ideally located on a spacious corner lot, combining privacy and convenience. The expansive outdoor area includes a storage shed, adding both functionality and storage solutions to your property. Inside, you'll discover two well-appointed bedrooms and an impeccably updated bathroom that embraces modern living standards without compromising the home's inherent charm. Every step within this residence is a delightful experience, thanks to the beautiful terrazzo floors that grace the living spaces, lending a timeless touch to the interiors. The modernized kitchen beckons you to showcase your culinary skills, with its contemporary updates designed to make cooking a pleasure. As you explore further, the indoor utility area promises to streamline your daily tasks, adding convenience to your busy life. Beyond the interior, a spacious covered and screened back porch eagerly awaits to host your tranquil mornings and relaxed evenings, setting the stage for countless cherished memories. Parking will never be a concern with the attached one-car carport and an extended driveway that provides ample space for your vehicle, ensuring easy access. From the front yard, you can enjoy picturesque views of Lake Deer, offering a serene backdrop to your everyday living. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood known for its minimal traffic, this home stands as a sanctuary amid the hustle and bustle of life. For first-time homebuyers, this residence is more than just a house; it's a stepping stone towards a delightful future filled with comfort and serenity. Adding to its appeal, the property features city sewer and water connections, along with an irrigation well, ensuring seamless living that seamlessly integrates nature and modernity. Embark on a journey of blissful living at 130 E Lake Deer Dr., where each day promises peace, comfort, and scenic beauty, inviting you to call it home.
